dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Johnny Foster. May I please have your name?
Hi, my name is Natalie Kelly.
Hello, Natalie. Could you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is six five seven eight two and my date of birth is zero five one eight nine zero three.
Thank you, Natalie. One last thing, could you confirm your mailing address for our records, starting with the house number?
Of course, my house number is nine nine four two, followed by Cedar Street, Los Angeles, California.
Thank you for confirming, Natalie. Is there anything else I can assist you with today regarding your policy or a new claim?
No, everything seems fine for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Natalie. Should you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Goodbye.
